#
# --- COMMIT MESSAGE GUIDELINES ---
# Type: feat|fix|refactor|test|docs|ci|style|perf|chore
# Scope: auth|backtest|optimize|market|tracking|ui|api
# Subject: Use imperative mood, lowercase, no period, max 50 chars
# 
# Example:
#   feat(backtest): add DCA strategy support
#   fix(optimize): correct sharpe ratio calculation
#   docs(api): update portfolio endpoints documentation
